---
import MainLayout from "@layouts/MainLayout.astro"
import Picture from "astro/components/Picture.astro"
import mainPhoto from "@assets/me.webp"
---

<MainLayout pageTitle="About me">
    <main class="main-container">
        <h1 class="title">Every composition answers a question.</h1>

        <div class="text-container">
            <p>I work where intention becomes form. Every project begins with listening, understanding context, constraints, and the message beneath the surface. From there, design is built with precision: structure, rhythm, and typography aligned to communicate without excess.</p>

            <p><b>My practice is grounded in user-centered visual communication, shaped by experience across corporate and editorial work</b>. I have led design teams, directed creative processes, and delivered projects within real constraints: time, scope, and clarity. That discipline is not only in me, but in every decision making clear that nothing is placed without purpose.</p>

            <p>Teaching has been part of this path. Guiding others through design fundamentals, creative thinking, and professional tools has reinforced a simple principle: clarity is learned through doing, not theory alone. This belief carries into my own work. My process is visible, and decisions are deliberate.</p>

            <p>I approach design as a system of relationships. Image, type, and space are not separate elements, but parts of a single voice. The goal is not to decorate, but to construct meaning.</p>

            <p>And that is all about for me: <span class="impact-text">works that holds, communicates, and endures beyond its surface.</span></p>
        </div>

        <div class="image-container">
            <Picture
                    src={mainPhoto}
                    formats={['avif', 'webp']}
                    alt="Manuel Pavón"
            />
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
    .main-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-align: left;
    }
    .text-container {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    .impact-text {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: var(--color-secondary);
    }

    .image-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px;
    }

    .image-container img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        filter: grayscale(100%);

        &:hover {
            filter: grayscale(0%);
            transition: filter 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .main-container {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .title {
            text-align: center;
        }
    }

</style>